      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "EASY RED (3) has been good in two runs to date, finishing third on each occasion, beaten just a neck last start at Mornington. 1600m here shouldn't pose an issue and Stockdale gets a lovely run up on the speed from barrier two. PARERA (2) presents third up here having made good improvement at Mornington when getting home well for a distant second behind a dominant winner. He can land in a good spot here and go one better. OLYMPIA FIELDS (8) ran a much better race over this route last time out when getting into third at a big quote. She too draws low and can settle handy with winning claims. TEMU TILLY (10) was okay behind a smart winner at Yarra Valley last time and is in the mix ahead of PASIFAE (9) who could improve.",
